---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <h1>About Me</h1>

  <p>
    I am an automation student at HDU-ITMO, interested in computer vision, robotic perception,
    embedded systems, and artificial intelligence that interacts with the physical world.
  </p>

  <p>
    In computer vision, I focus on OpenCV, CNN-based methods, YOLO object detection, and the
    deployment of vision models on edge devices. In robotics, I am interested in low-level
    control systems such as STM32 and Arduino, as well as ROS1 / ROS2 communication, navigation,
    SLAM, and multi-sensor perception.
  </p>

  <p>
    My long-term goal is to connect AI algorithms with real-world physical systems and build
    intelligent robotic systems that can perceive, reason, and act in real environments.
  </p>

  <section>
    <h2>Education</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>HDU-ITMO Automation Program</h3>
      <p>
        Joint undergraduate program in Automation between Hangzhou Dianzi University and
        ITMO University, focusing on control systems, robotics, computer vision, and
        embedded intelligent systems.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Research Interests</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <ul>
        <li>Computer Vision</li>
        <li>Embedded AI</li>
        <li>Robotics</li>
        <li>Visual SLAM</li>
        <li>Navigation</li>
        <li>Physics-informed Modeling</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Engineering Interests</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <ul>
        <li>STM32 / Arduino</li>
        <li>ROS1 / ROS2</li>
        <li>YOLO Deployment</li>
        <li>RKNN Quantization</li>
        <li>Real-time Vision Systems</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
